<H4>    Foreign Help for Sci-Tech Center </H4>

<F P=102> 94UM0382A Kiev NARODNA ARMIYA in Ukrainian 3 Nov 93 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0382A </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev NARODNA ARMIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


