<H4>    Warhead Material for Reactor Fuel </H4>

<F P=102> 94UM0382B Kiev NARODNA ARMIYA in Ukrainian 16 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0382B </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev NARODNA ARMIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
