<H3> <TI>   Chernommyrdin Remarks at Dedication of Destroyer </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chernommyrdin Remarks at Dedication of Destroyer </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
`Beshtrashnyy' 

<F P=102>   944D0015B Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 19 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944D0015B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>
