<H3> <TI>   Latvian Sejm Refuses to Approve Agreement With Russia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Latvian Sejm Refuses to Approve Agreement With Russia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944D0007B Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 22 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
